HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sabbin masu cutar.
China ta ba da rahoton kashi 14 cikin 100 na karuwar mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, in ji hukumomin lafiya.
An yi rajistar sabbin cututtukan cutar sama da 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin lokuta ana daukar su ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji daga baya.
A al'ada, HIV ya yadu cikin sauri a wasu yankuna na China sakamakon gurɓataccen jinin jini.
Amma yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanya ya ragu kusan zuwa babu, kamar yadda jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin suka fada a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya karu da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin ne a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga 'yan LGBTI ya ci gaba da zama gama gari.
A sakamakon dabi'un ra'ayin mazan jiya na kasar, bincike ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70-90 cikin dari na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtuka da ake yadawa ta hanyar jima'i saboda rashin amfani da kariya ta jima'i.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ba da umarnin samun damar yin amfani da maganin HIV a ko'ina a kokarin magance matsalar.
