Wannan Asabar, New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin 'yan kasa na duniya, bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke tattara manyan masu fasaha da kuma samun babban manufa na duniya, don kawar da talauci a duniya.
Wannan bikin, wanda aka gudanar a karo na goma sha bakwai, zai kawo dubban mutane zuwa Babban Filin a Central Park, ba kawai don jin dadin wasan kwaikwayon da masu zane-zane irin su Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes, amma kuma don fadakar da mutane game da ainihin manufar wannan taron, wanda shine kawar da matsanancin talauci kafin 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka kafa a 2012, ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, ƙungiyar tallafi ta ƙasa da ƙasa wacce ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar haɓaka yawan mutanen da ke aiki da talauci.
Don samun kyauta kyauta zuwa taron (idan ba a shirya ku ba don biyan kuɗin VIP), waɗanda suke so su halarci wasan kwaikwayo suna buƙatar yin ayyuka da dama ko "ayyuka", kamar aikawa da sakon imel zuwa wani shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko kuma yin kira a wasu hanyoyi masu amfani don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya za a ce ya yi nasara a Global Citizen lokacin da ya rage shekaru 12 kawai don cimma burinsa?
Shin wannan ra'ayin da ya karfafa mutane su nemi wani abu ta hanyar yin wasan kwaikwayo kyauta, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" wato, sanya mutane su ji suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu a kan wata takarda ko kuma ta hanyar aika da sako ta Twitter?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya yi rikodin sama da "ayyuka" miliyan 19 daga mabiyansa, yana turawa don cimma manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce, shugabannin duniya sun tattaro kansu don sanar da manufofi da alkawura masu darajar sama da dala biliyan 37 kuma waɗannan manufofi da alkawuran za su shafi rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 kafin shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ba da sanarwar alkawura da sanarwa 390 da suka samo asali daga ayyukan, wanda akalla dala biliyan 10 aka biya ko karɓa.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka ba da tabbacin sun yi tasiri kai tsaye a kan mutane miliyan 649 a duk duniya.
