Bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar EEU da ke tallata cinikayya mai amfani tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ambaci karin kudin da ya biya wa jaridar Des Moines Register, wacce ita ce jarida ta biyu mafi yawan sayarwa a jihar Iowa a ranar Laraba bayan da ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da aka gudanar a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ke musantawa.
Trump ya yi tsokaci kan zargin cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, wani sabon yunkuri ne na matsawa China a Washington.
Duk da cewa ba abin mamaki ba ne ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace don bunkasa kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a yanzu haka sun makale a cikin yakin cinikayya da ke ci gaba wanda a cikinsa kowace ƙasa ke sanya takunkumi kan shigo da kayayyakin ɗayan.
