Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, daya daga cikin jihohin da suka fi fitar da kayayyakin noma zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kuma kasuwancin Amurka.
Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wata kasida a cikin Sunday's Des Moines Register cewa, "China yanzu tana kara kai hari ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yancinmu na' yanci".
