"A akasin wannan, a nan a rumfar 'yan jarida a kan titin Beijing, akwai muryoyi kalilan da suka nuna rashin amincewa kuma babu wani gaskiya game da ra'ayoyi daban-daban da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya yi game da yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon Jam'iyyar Kwaminisancin kasar Sin".
