Saboda tsarin sadarwa ya lalace, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun bayanai daga gwamnatin Donggala, yankin da ke kusa da girgizar ƙasa mai girman 7.5, arewacin Pallu.
Sama da mutane 16,000 ne aka kwashe bayan wannan bala'i.
Ga wasu bayanai masu mahimmanci game da garin Palu da kuma gwamnatin Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Central Sulawesi, kuma yana kusa da ƙarshen gabar tekun a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi; a cikin 2017, yana da kusan mutane 379,800.
Lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka faru, garin yana bikin bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa.
Donggala, a gefe guda, ita ce gwamnati da ke rufe fiye da kilomita 300 (180 mi) wanda ke rufe bakin tekun arewa maso yamma na tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gwamnati, wanda shine yankin da ke ƙarƙashin ikon lardin, yana da yawan mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Tattalin arzikin lardin Central Sulawesi ya dogara ne akan kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
